Slinky provides high-performance web crawler and text analytics in Python.

  * uses Redis key/value store for both URL Queue and Page Store
  * uses Hadoop, R, Gephi for text analytics and link analytics


Requires:
	http://github.com/andymccurdy/redis-py
	http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/

Usage:
	cat urls.txt | ./slinky.py redis_host:port:db [ flush | seed | whitelist | crawl ]
